For instructions on nominating a page for deletion, please refer to the [deletion policy](/Wikipedia:Deletion_policy) or the [Guide to deletion](/Wikipedia:Guide_to_deletion).

This page isn't just some casual read; it meticulously documents an English Wikipedia [deletion guideline](/Category:Wikipedia_deletion_guidelines). Editors are generally expected to adhere to its tenets, though, as with most rules, [exceptions](/Wikipedia:Ignore_all_rules) occasionally apply for those bold enough to claim them. Any significant alterations to this page, naturally, [should reflect consensus](/Wikipedia:PGCHANGE) – because even the most tedious processes demand a modicum of collective agreement.

